text: Eberhard Kneisl (12 May 1916 - 26 December 2008) was an Austrian alpine skier. He competed in two events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Austrian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Austria Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tyrol (state)
